在1953年版的《[[泰坦尼克号_(1953年电影)|泰坦尼克号]]》中出现了这首赞美诗<ref>{{cite book |first=Jeffrey |last = Richards |authorlink=Jeffrey Richards |title = A Night to remember: the definitive Titanic film |publisher = [[I.B._Tauris|I.B. Tauris]] |location = [[London|London]] |year=2003 |page = [http://books.google.com/books?id=fQprnv2xTKIC&pg=PA26 26] |isbn = 1-86064-849-5 |oclc = 55898225}}</ref>。

该赞美诗的中文版常编在华人教会诗歌本的第一首。[[中国基督教协会|中国基督教协会]]出版的《[[赞美诗（新编）|赞美诗（新编）]]》收录该诗歌，列为第1首。

== 歌词 ==
=== 英语 ===
<poem>
Holy, Holy, Holy! Lord God Almighty!
Early in the morning our song shall rise to Thee;
Holy, Holy, Holy! Merciful and Mighty!
God in Three Persons, blessed Trinity! 

Holy, Holy, Holy! all the saints adore Thee,
Casting down their golden crowns around the glassy sea;
Cherubim and Seraphim falling down before Thee,
Which wert, and art, and evermore shalt be.

Holy, Holy, Holy! though the darkness hide Thee,
Though the eye of sinful man Thy glory may not see:
Only Thou art holy, there is none beside Thee,
Perfect in power, in love, and purity.

Holy, Holy, Holy! Lord God Almighty!
All Thy works shall praise thy name in earth and sky and sea;
Holy, Holy, Holy! Merciful and Mighty!
God in Three Persons, blessed Trinity! 
</poem>

=== 中文 ===
出版：中國基督教協會<br>
收錄於《讚美詩(新編)》第1首

1.聖哉，聖哉，聖哉，全能大主宰！<br>
清晨我众歌声，穿云上达至尊；<br>
圣哉，圣哉，圣哉！慈悲与全能，<br>
荣耀于赞美，归三一妙身。<br>

2.圣哉，圣哉，圣哉！众圣都崇敬，<br>
放下黄金冠冕，环绕晶海之滨；<br>
千万天军叩拜，同声颂主名，<br>
昔在而今在，永在亿万春。<br>

3.圣哉，圣哉，圣哉！黑暗蔽圣明，<br>
罪人不能仰视庄严广大妙身；<br>
唯独主为真原，惟主为至尊，<br>
全权又全爱，全善全能神。<br>

4.圣哉，圣哉，圣哉！全权的神明！<br>
海天云山酬和吾众赞美歌声；<br>
圣哉，圣哉，圣哉！慈悲与全能，<br>
荣耀与赞美，归三一妙身。<br>

（阿们）

